OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FA cold and rather bright
OL,6,Fstart. Becoming increasingly cloudy
OL,7,Fthrough the morning and afternoon,
OL,8,Fwith a chance of isolated showers
OL,9,Flater in the day. Winds remaining
OL,10,Flargely light.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FDry
OL,13,Fwith sunny spells Tuesday and
OL,14,FWednesday. Cloudy start Thursday,
OL,15,Fclearing later. Breezy, perhaps strong
OL,16,Fover hills. Warm, though cooler near
OL,17,Feastern coasts. Chilly by night.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
